CatDescriptText: Cutline of article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 18, 1960, pg. 5 reads: "Nearly Five Thousand Persons jammed the Syria Mosque, site of the three-day Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama, June 7-8-9."
TitMainTitle: Four piece band performing on stage of the Natural Gas Companies appliance booth in Syria Mosque for the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama
